tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE real_estate_investment_returns (
  investment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  property_name VARCHAR(255),
  property_type VARCHAR(50),
  purchase_price DECIMAL(10,2),
  purchase_date TIMESTAMP,
  sale_price DECIMAL(10,2),
  sale_date TIMESTAMP,
  return_on_investment DECIMAL(5,2),
  market_performance_analysis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE real_estate_properties (
  property_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  property_address TEXT NOT NULL,
  purchase_price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  purchase_date DATE,
  annual_rental_income DECIMAL,
  operating_expenses DECIMAL,
  property_type TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE investment_returns (
  return_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  property_id UUID REFERENCES real_estate_properties(property_id),
  return_date DATE,
  total_return DECIMAL,
  annualized_return DECIMAL,
  ROI DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE real_estate_properties (
  property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  property_name VARCHAR(255),
  purchase_price DECIMAL,
  market_value DECIMAL,
  return_on_investment DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE investment_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  property_id INT,
  investment_date DATE,
  investment_return DECIMAL,
  FOREIGN KEY (property_id) REFERENCES real_estate_properties(property_id)
);

CREATE TABLE real_estate_properties (
    property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_name TEXT,
    purchase_price DECIMAL,
    purchase_date DATE,
    property_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE investment_returns (
    return_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT,
    investor_id INT,
    return_amount DECIMAL,
    return_date DATE
);
